dev-1.x.name: drupal/ckeditor_browser_context_menu

security-coverage.message: Project has not opted into security advisory coverage!

dev-1.x.description: Makes CKEditor use the browser's built-in context menu instead of CKEditor's custom context menu (right-click menu).  This will allow full use of the browser's built-in spellcheck capabilities.  NOTE: This disables the contextmenu, tabletools, and tableresize plugins.
